Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll head in first while you find parking, Takahiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, I'll be in soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Tsubaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:35.67,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H22433D&\3c&HB3DFA0&\3a&H00&\pos(182,110)}Sumiya piano recitals
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we've come here as guests, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure has. It's nice not having to be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That dress looks really good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's get a photo taken together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Secchan's daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take a photo of me and Secchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, stand there next to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go. Say "Cheese!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:23.61,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}The rainbow after a storm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.61,0:01:26.77,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}And the flowers blooming by the wayside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:32.03,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}Burst into color that day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:38.06,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}When I saw you gazing at the crimson sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:44.09,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}And fell in love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.09,0:01:47.11,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}Every dramatic frame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:50.20,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}We painted on that film roll
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:55.26,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}Will stay forever etched
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:59.00,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}In my memories
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:02.04,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}It was you, my special one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:04.97,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}It was you who opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.94,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}The stars in the night sky show us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:10.99,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}There can be light in darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:13.85,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}Stop hiding your sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:17.02,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}Behind that dazzling smile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:19.85,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}For all the stars in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:23.01,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}Shine brightly on you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:28.27,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,150)}The hopes and fears we cling to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:36.01,OP English Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(150,1400)}Will be the guiding lights that lead us into brilliance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You always get a soda ice block, don't you Emi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it tasty, Emi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mako-chan's going up 7th, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to hear her play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked really nervous. Is she going to be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to go and play dodgeball with Yuuichi and everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up Watari, it's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a really pretty lady—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:10.60,Secondary line,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Number 5, Arima Kousei-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth happened, Emi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You ran out of there before even listening to Mako-chan play!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Number 5, Arima Kousei-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Arima...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...Kousei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to—Woah, hey, that's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to climb, do it on the slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become a pianist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:51.82,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4B4847&\3c&HF9FDFD&\3a&H00&\fad(500,0)\pos(574.132,93.5)}Primary schoolers' \Npiano competition
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:51.82,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4B4847&\3c&HF9FDFD&\3a&H00&\fad(500,0)\pos(556.698,48.125)}Sumiya district
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But you play the violin, Kao-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to play when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go shopping after we watch for a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but just for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Arima Kousei-kun's gonna win again, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,With Arima-kun here, I feel bad for the children competing in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because he... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...isn't Arima Kousei!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arima?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why's he alone? Doesn't he have anyone with him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my chance to get close to him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll have an ice block!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is the kind that splits in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can eat both!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's ignoring me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Ochiai-Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My, what a surprise it is to see you here, Takayanagi-Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a child I'm teaching right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This power-hungry snob is teaching a primary schooler?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Aiza Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a very promising future ahead of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you're teaching a piano class now—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,—Oh, but I suppose it is more your area of expertise to be coaching young children...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Children can be very difficult to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be drained dry if you don't know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,By the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your advice sure pains me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I'm simply giving you a friendly warning.
