Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get a Transformation Belt just for competing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if I win, I'll get the Super Mech!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Piano's a breeze!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Incredible! He's incredible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He plays the sheet music perfectly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone's so on edge, but he doesn't even raise an eyebrow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's just like one of those Western cowboys!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A heart of steel, and unmatched skill!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He leaves the stage without smiling or saying a word!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's like a Super Mech Robot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's super strong, and super cool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arima{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is a hero!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I made another mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I play like he does?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what kind of practice does he do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has he been rebuilt on the inside?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takayanagi-Sensei just makes me play the same song over and over again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what his secret is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be around here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where Hibari Primary School is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go straight that way, and then down the second alleyway on your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of alleyways around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's easy to get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a cakery?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're planning on opening next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma-Ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma Fille.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It means "my daughter" in French.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing. Stop by once we're open!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:15.70,Default top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}See ya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.30,Default top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye-bye!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My school doesn't have classes today because of an event{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I've gotta make the most of this chance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's Arima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:36.06,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}Hey, turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:36.57,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H746C5B&\3a&H00&\pos(294.717,131.175)\fs29.7}Arima
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:39.76,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}Hey, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:43.30,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}You're not small, and you're not weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:48.70,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}In fact, I think you've grown a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.70,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H223044&\3c&H5A9DC3&\3a&H28&\fs29.7\pos(386.868,104.775)}Sawabe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:52.58,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}See? You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:56.38,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}See? Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:11:05.00,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}Embrace that shining light of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's hear you practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:14.72,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}There are days when I can't seem to catch up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow. He's been going for a whole hour.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:21.58,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}But I know that it's going to be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How is he able to keep playing for so long without making any mistakes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has incredible concentration.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:31.80,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}I'm not doing this for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:35.58,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}I'm just doing this so that I can keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:42.18,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}I'll do everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been doing repetitive practice this whole time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sun's gonna go down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:51.86,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}I desperately clung to your back because I longed to be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:59.44,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}I tried to pretend that I was fine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He plays the same song over and over again for hours. It must be so tiring. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:07.54,Senobi,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.125\fad(200,200)}but in the end, my heart still pains a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Burning the music into his body,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}repeating the same movements over and over again,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in order to play a perfect manifestation of the score.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:42.57,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H34393B&\pos(260.679,192.225)\3c&HE2E8E9&\3a&H00&}#2 Aiza Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:42.57,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H34393B&\pos(248.226,289.575)}#3 Igawa Emi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:42.57,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H34393B&\pos(263.17,96.525)\3c&HE3E9EA&\3a&H00&}#1 Arima Kousei
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:40.90,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H303232&\move(362.792,254.925,362.792,14.85,29,1322)}Preliminary round placings
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow! He's 1st place again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit. It's not enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's nowhere near enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:52.83,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2F322F&\3c&HECF4F1&\3a&H00&\pos(483.17,153.45)}Ueuchi Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:52.83,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2F322F&\3c&HECF4F1&\3a&H00&\pos(443.321,183.15)}Final round
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I woke up really early,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and practiced for at least 5 hours every single day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that I perfectly replicated the score!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's alright. I'm a Super Mech too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Start off slow and melancholic, and invoke unease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, play wistfully, \Nlike a warm Springtime sunset."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's she doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Number 5, Igawa-san, please make your preparations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Got something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was with that performance?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She completely ignored the score!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why is everyone cheering?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like that, Fake Arima?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.19,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\move(352,256.575,352,12.375,20,1188)\fad(500,0)\c&H3D3D3B&}Final round placings
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.40,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3C3B39&\move(441.66,385.275,441.66,10.725,23,1858)}Arima Kousei
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.99,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3C3B39&\move(441.66,385.275,441.66,16.5,23,2023)}Igawa Emi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.99,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3C3B39&\pos(445.811,373.725)\3c&HFDFCFA&\3a&H00&}Aiza Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You managed to secure a placing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:27.88,placings,,0,0,0,,{\c&H676969&\3c&HEEEFEF&\3a&H00&\pos(234.113,112.2)}Final round placings\N\N#1 Arima Kousei\N#4 Igawa Emi\N#10 Aiza Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Arima's a monster known as the Tempest of the Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, you'll also be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's her. She's the one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's throwing me off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Igawa Emi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.46,Default top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye-bye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We need one more person. Wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I forgot I have piano practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Next time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I even gave up soccer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm waking up early and practicing for 5 hours!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm even practicing during the holidays!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't need any new toys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't even hang out with my friends!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...become an invincible hero too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to hear Arima's disciplined music!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that I don't have an unwavering resolve like him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that I need to put in more effort!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's doing a lot more than I am!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even right now, he's probably tuned to his piano, alone, with his heart of steel—!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:58.64,Default top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go on, Kousei!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Kousei! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arima?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do a summersault this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to jump again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was awesome, Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.26,Secondary line,,0,0,0,,I'm next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.66,Secondary line,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna jump too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...what he looks like when he smiles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna play soccer tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:51.31,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fs14.85\pos(578.642,253.275)\3c&H765741&\3a&H00&\c&H180D00&}Saiki Piano Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:51.31,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fs14.85\3c&H765741&\3a&H00&\c&H180D00&\pos(563.698,271.425)}Preliminary round
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:54.32,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H535451&\frz17.61\pos(272.302,66.825)}Saiki Piano Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:54.32,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H535451&\frz17.61\pos(450.792,102.3)}Preliminary round placings
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:54.32,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H535451&\frz15.05\pos(388.528,205.425)}Arima Kousei
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:54.32,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H535451&\pos(390.189,269.775)\frz13.44}Aiza Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:54.32,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H535451&\frz11.23\pos(394.34,336.6)}Igawa Emi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course Arima still wins again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect playing, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even come close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you frustrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I decided that I'm gonna take him out in the second round
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,when there are more people watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care. I was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I always choose a piece that Arima's likely to play,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but my prediction was off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't really care,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,since we're not gonna be playing the same piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want to go up against Arima with the same piece? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great sportsmanship! And really manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not about winning or losing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...want him to come back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been practicing a little too hard lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You said, before,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that if I wish strongly enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the music will speak to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That the piano will begin to play on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:30.21,sonata title,,0,0,0,,{\c&H999997&\frz10.67\fs23.1\move(275.623,174.9,255.698,174.9,2,3589)}Beethoven: Piano sonata No. 23 in F minor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:30.21,sonata title,,0,0,0,,{\c&H999997&\frz10.67\fs23.1\move(363.623,222.75,359.472,226.875,2,3589)}3rd movement
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:30.21,sonata title,,0,0,0,,{\c&H999997&\fs29.7\b1\frz10.14\move(200.075,79.2,176,70.125,2,3589)}Arima Kousei{\b0} (Age 10)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beethoven's 23rd sonata, "Appassionata," 3rd movement.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...want to let the piano play!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just following the score like always.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The invincible Arima Kousei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But today, I'll show him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make him remember, with my own hands:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who he really is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:00.94,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4F4D4B&\fad(500,0)\move(383.547,258.225,383.547,2.475,28,1988)}Arima Kousei
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You did alright today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your baby gonna be born yet, Hiro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt a kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby kicks you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the baby's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take her to see a doctor tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We will. I'm sorry about this, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise for not noticing sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say anything if your hands were hurting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they building something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:04.34,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(340.377,41.25)\c&H454747&}Moriwaki
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:04.34,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H454747&\pos(295.547,62.7)}Piano Competition
