Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you had tendonitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all better?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know I can still play just as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's not what I was asking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still eating that same ice block even though you're in grade 6 now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not one to talk. You were eating that when I first saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna keep playing the piano
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all through middle school
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and even through high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,After having to stop playing the piano for a while, I learned something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I really love playing the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the way Arima feels too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! How would I know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you getting mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch, Arima!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you cry "Uncle!" with the power I've stored up while not being able to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arima!{\i0}
